<h3 id="toc0"><span>叶樱与魔笛</span></h3>
<h1 id="toc1"><span><span style="color: red"><strong>FBI Warning</strong></span></span></h1>
<h2 id="toc2"><span>本篇含有一定的成人内容，请酌情阅读</span></h2>
</div>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5090298&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569470" alt="The Obsidian Shard" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5090298)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-obsidian-shard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5090298); return false;">The Obsidian Shard</a></span>以及他的<a href="/the-obsidian-shard">更多作品</a></p>
<p><strong>题目来源：</strong>取材于太宰治的同名小说<em>叶樱与魔笛</em>，本篇与其除题目外没有任何关系，这只是对我所喜爱的作家的致敬，所以即便没有读过也不会有任何影响。</p>
<p><strong>文中彩蛋：</strong>请移步至<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/forum/t-13159732/wanderers:hazakura-to-mabue">评论区</a></p>
<p><strong>图片来源：</strong><span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sbshansh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2898660); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2898660&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569470" alt="sbshansh" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2898660)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sbshansh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2898660); return false;">sbshansh</a></span>在画廊中提供的照片：<a href="https://i.loli.net/2020/02/01/XIA8EuO964xnrBN.jpg">https://i.loli.net/2020/02/01/XIA8EuO964xnrBN.jpg</a>，我将其进行了调色的简单二次创作，不违反本次竞赛规则。</span><br />
换图后图片来源：<a href="https://pixabay.com/photos/sunset-clouds-lake-rest-sunny-192978/">https://pixabay.com/photos/sunset-clouds-lake-rest-sunny-192978/</a></p>
<p><strong>以及各种其他来源：</strong>吹笛人的字体为”Long Cang“，主题版式为<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/component:dustjacket-theme">封护</a>与<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/wanderers:wanderers-station">流浪者站</a>，侧边栏进行了<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/component:bhl-dark-sidebar">暗色</a>调整</p>
